{"tid":335381,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"［黃金黑店］比間黑店呃左張switch記憶卡","createTime":"2017-07-25T13:56:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-30T04:34:41.000Z","uid":12182,"like":11,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"799c79e20161120740d345413a0b44bc7c048a7a","tid":335381,"uid":12182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T13:56:42.000Z","msg":"利申 我係on9仔 冇即場驗收<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n是咁的，話說前幾日買係黃金買左部switch <br />\n順手買埋張專用記憶卡，咁個店員就幫我插左張卡入去update<br />\n當時冇留意佢插左張咩卡入去部機到<br />\n返到屋企拆出黎先發現佢將張卡換左張San disk32gb卡入去<br />\n就係咁就比人呃左<br />\n<br />\n我就預左張卡換唔返，只希望各位巴打小心<br />\n一齊抵制黑店<br />\n<br />\n黑店名: G.WORXSHOX<br />\n位置：黃金商場上層（近地鐵站出口）果幾間<br />\n補充一句 當時我碌卡，佢拎左張卡去隔離間鋪到碌，相信隔離果幾間都有機會係蛇鼠一窩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/25/215535_2035bfd0359f830b6ab87b04501382c7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F25%2F215535_2035bfd0359f830b6ab87b04501382c7.jpg&h=c3b19ff1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/25/215541_daac68d33a46831e71e6b282fe7d8d45.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F25%2F215541_daac68d33a46831e71e6b282fe7d8d45.jpg&h=97e22580&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d9201432202d229d5387284d145b7ff4f0043d41","tid":335381,"uid":16061,"like":18,"dislike":3,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T14:10:07.000Z","msg":"重有人去黃金買機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f12f983eea3a3b42ca9560ab0fcb2848be1ae8f5","tid":335381,"uid":118502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T14:12:20.000Z","msg":"我係呢間鋪左近到買，玻璃貼收我240"},{"pid":"90b6af5a510bfdb19e85ff81af72072fbeb0f33a","tid":335381,"uid":130513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T14:13:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1518dbaa13f4fc311020043146d6498bcd04c4d3","tid":335381,"uid":12182,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score"